                     <interp inst="t17541023-33-person229" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , cast now for transportation, another is 
               <persName id="t17541023-33-person230">
                  James 
                  Clark 
               <interp inst="t17541023-33-person230" type="surname" value="Clark"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17541023-33-person230" type="given" value="James"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17541023-33-person230" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , and another 
               <persName id="t17541023-33-person231">
                  John 
                  Hanks 
               <interp inst="t17541023-33-person231" type="surname" value="Hanks"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17541023-33-person231" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17541023-33-person231" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            .</p>
               <p>Furner. At the time he was taken he pretended to be a stranger to the others.</p>
